                Colin Crawford, masterâ¬"s student in film studies,http://www.concordia.ca/news/stories/2019/02/01/concordians-receive-3m-in-federal-funding-for-social-sciences-and-humanities-research/_jcr_content/top-image.img.768.medium.jpg/1548953218374.jpg class="container grid-narrow">
